qsstv (9.5.13-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Replace HB9HFJ TX pre-emphasis IIR with linear-phase FIR
    (51-tap, tau=750us, +23dB plateau above 3 kHz, group delay 0.52 ms)
  * Remove obsolete 50/75 us tau combobox from sound config
  * Clean up LDPC/turbo remnants in DRM RX status frame, profile config,
    parameter structures, and dead code paths
  * Recompute image and TX duration on DRM preset change (re-encode with
    new codec/resolution before TX)
  * Fix all compiler warnings (-Wuse-after-free in Matlib, deprecated
    OpenJPEG bpp field, unused parameter in MLC)

 -- HB9TOB <hb9tob@hb9tob.ch>  Mon, 27 Apr 2026 17:15:00 +0200

qsstv (9.5.12-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Remove LDPC / turbo FEC code, Viterbi is the only DRM FEC
  * AVIF image codec support (independent of FEC, JP2/AVIF selector)
  * HB9HFJ-style TX pre-emphasis filter (50/75 us, configurable)
  * Duplicate TX audio L->R when PTT tone channel is disabled
  * Windows PortAudio backend
  * QSerialPort for cross-platform PTT

 -- HB9TOB <hb9tob@hb9tob.ch>  Mon, 20 Apr 2026 19:45:00 +0200

qsstv (10.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * LDPC forward error correction (WiFi 802.11n QC-LDPC codes)
  * AVIF image codec support (independent of FEC mode)
  * WiFi-style MSC payload sizing for LDPC mode
  * PRBS run-in/run-out for LDPC pipeline
  * Windows PortAudio backend
  * QSerialPort for cross-platform PTT

